s for secretary of state.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:6.0pt">One other name mention=
ed by several Republicans as a possible Trump Treasury secretary is Glenn H=
ubbard, currently dean of the Columbia University Graduate School of Busine=
ss. Hubbard served in top economic jobs
