a governor dropped out of the 2016 campaign.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:6.0pt">Trump would certainly =
not be Hubbard&#8217;s first choice of presidents to serve, people who know=
 him said. But he might agree if implored by Trump to help run economic pol=
icy including a big tax rewrite, Hubbard&#8217;s
