 of him.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:6.0pt">During a foreign polic=
y address last month in Washington, Trump signaled he had little interest i=
n many of the Bush administration veterans who have been busy during the Ob=
ama era making money at law firms, on
 K Street and in academia since leaving their government jobs, many more th=
an a decade ago.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:6.0pt">&#8220;We have to look=
 to new people because many of the old people frankly don&#8217;t know what=
 they&#8217;re doing, even though they may look awfully good writing in The=
 New York Times or being watched on television,&#8221; Trump
 said.<o:p></o:p></p>
